main event: Several objects were sighted flying in formation over Vashon, Washington on 13 September 1965.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 20 seconds., The observer noted that there were three objects., No physical evidence was obtained from the sighting., The report concluded that there was insufficient data for evaluation., The sighting occurred at 9:03 PST.
witness description: a civilian residing on Vashon Island
